Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:41.13,0:01:42.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好美的星星啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:42.80,0:01:43.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:43.93,0:01:48.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tim，总有一天会有人从那片星海中来迎接你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:48.67,0:01:49.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,来迎接我？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:49.80,0:01:54.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没错．这片星空上的某个地方有个很想念你的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:55.41,0:01:56.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是呢，Tim
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:56.84,0:01:58.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不要忘记
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:58.25,0:01:59.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:01.82,0:02:06.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,第七话 试练
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:07.15,0:02:09.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这位是Timothy·Constance先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:09.69,0:02:10.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l3岁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:10.62,0:02:12.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,出生于Primavera行星
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:12.59,0:02:14.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,其母是Marianne·Constance
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:15.13,0:02:16.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而他的父亲是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:16.63,0:02:19.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ablert·Rosenfelt
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:19.47,0:02:25.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ablert·Rosenfelt，最近去世的Rosenfelt财团族长
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:25.94,0:02:27.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rosenfelt财团？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:28.14,0:02:33.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,总资产占全银河系金融总额的6.82%
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:34.01,0:02:37.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,最新的统计显示为7.14%
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:37.78,0:02:40.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哦～那他是大少爷啰？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:42.16,0:02:43.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Timothy·Constance先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:43.99,0:02:45.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Albert先生留下了遗言
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:46.03,0:02:48.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,指定他为下一任继承人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:48.53,0:02:50.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不过必须在指定的期限内
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:51.16,0:02:54.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在特定的地方确认是他本人 这件事情才算成立
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:55.74,0:02:56.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,以标准时间来看的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:56.90,0:02:59.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还有36小时l3分58秒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:00.67,0:03:02.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果无法确认的话…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:02.58,0:03:04.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,继承的资格就会被取消
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:04.91,0:03:07.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哇～那多可惜啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:08.05,0:03:10.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,之后有关系的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:10.28,0:03:12.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就会为了事业、权力展开争夺吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:13.09,0:03:16.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,本来应该要同时通知指定地点的所在地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:16.52,0:03:18.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是因为资料受损
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:18.46,0:03:20.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,导致无法辨识正确地点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:20.93,0:03:23.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,虽然已经故意对外放出假消息
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:23.63,0:03:27.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但金融管理局似乎在背后进行了一些动作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:28.07,0:03:29.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们的特别任务
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:29.80,0:03:33.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是在修复的情报中找出原本被指定的行星
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:33.37,0:03:36.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在期限之内将Constance先生平安送达
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:37.24,0:03:39.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可以当成线索的只有这些吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:39.95,0:03:41.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,DNA鉴定之地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:42.02,0:03:45.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就在Albert·Rosenfelt所诞生的行星…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:45.95,0:03:47.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lumiere 怎么样？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:47.59,0:03:50.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还在用网络搜寻中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:50.26,0:03:53.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,寻找个人情报是很不容易的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:53.43,0:03:55.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不过 本来就不可能太简单吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:56.80,0:04:00.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,且是上流社会的人的话那就更是难上加难了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:02.04,0:04:03.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不用紧张喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:04.71,0:04:06.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Constance先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:06.64,0:04:09.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们会好好保住你的遗产继承权的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:10.91,0:04:12.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请不要叫我“先生”好吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:12.71,0:04:14.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,感觉好像不是我的名字似的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:15.88,0:04:16.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,找到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:17.95,0:04:19.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Boldor星系…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:19.89,0:04:22.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Farandole行星
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:22.76,0:04:25.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是在银河系的另一端呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:25.36,0:04:26.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只要经过空间跳跃一瞬间就到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:39.41,0:04:43.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,贫困的男孩子在魔法棒下摇身变成大富翁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:44.64,0:04:46.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯～好浪漫哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:46.61,0:04:48.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,简直就像是最近看过的故事书一样耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:48.82,0:04:49.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:53.32,0:04:54.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那 我们也走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:54.72,0:04:56.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要是跟丢的话 可是会被念个半死的哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:02.66,0:05:03.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,私奔？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:03.80,0:05:05.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸为了跟妈妈结婚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:06.23,0:05:07.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,放弃了继承权
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:07.87,0:05:11.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,曾经一度脱离了Ronsenfelt财团
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:11.64,0:05:15.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然後在Primavera行星从事农业
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:15.94,0:05:17.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那个时候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:17.31,0:05:20.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸用的是本名Cillford
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:21.28,0:05:24.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但最后父亲还是留下了我跟妈妈回家去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:24.72,0:05:28.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,承袭Albert之名成为家族之主
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:28.79,0:05:31.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我连父亲的容貌也不记得
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:32.03,0:05:35.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也不知道自己跟Ronsenfelt家族有关
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:36.56,0:05:38.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,自从妈妈去世以后
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:38.33,0:05:40.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我就一直在爷爷的农场工作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:40.93,0:05:45.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然後 最近GOTT来了消息
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:45.41,0:05:47.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,才第一次听爷爷谈起这件事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:49.58,0:05:52.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是 也真是个任性的父亲呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:52.41,0:05:54.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一直都放着你们母子不管
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:54.41,0:05:56.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等有了万一 又希望你能够继承他的位置
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:56.95,0:05:57.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,够啰…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:57.92,0:06:01.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且 还让你在GOTT或金融管理局
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:01.69,0:06:03.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这些大人们之间被叫来唤去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:03.72,0:06:05.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不…没这回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:29.42,0:06:30.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好像搞错地点了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:31.55,0:06:33.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会？搜寻的结果确实…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:36.06,0:06:39.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这里真的是你父亲的出生地？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:39.29,0:06:42.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不 我只知道爸爸的名字…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:42.86,0:06:44.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,名字？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:44.50,0:06:45.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,说不定…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:47.13,0:06:49.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸改用Albert这个名字
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:49.67,0:06:52.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是跟我和妈妈分开之后的事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:52.24,0:06:53.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对我而言
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:53.37,0:06:55.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Albert并不是我爸爸 而是陌生人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:56.64,0:06:57.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,出现了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:57.61,0:07:00.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sylvia星系的…Silvana行星？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:01.21,0:07:03.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是Tim的父亲成为第25代族长
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:04.08,0:07:05.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,继承Albert之名
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:05.49,0:07:09.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,并被认定为财团继承人的星球
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:11.02,0:07:13.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只剩两个标准小时
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:13.46,0:07:14.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,勉勉强强呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:17.13,0:07:18.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,陨石群接近
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:18.30,0:07:19.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,临时形成的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:20.47,0:07:21.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是漂亮的偶然呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:22.87,0:07:24.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这也是有人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:24.27,0:07:26.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 警告意味很强
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:26.27,0:07:27.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要是绕远路的话就会来不及
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:35.18,0:07:35.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没问题吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:36.08,0:07:36.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:37.55,0:07:38.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,害怕吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:38.65,0:07:39.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:39.75,0:07:42.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 男孩子就得这样才行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:42.39,0:07:43.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eclair
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:44.96,0:07:45.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,回避！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:45.66,0:07:46.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,来不及了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:50.13,0:07:51.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什…什么？刚刚那个…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:59.54,0:08:00.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗨～
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:00.67,0:08:01.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Viola！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:01.54,0:08:02.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cesario
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:03.14,0:08:04.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小Lumi、小Ec
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:04.64,0:08:06.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好久不见了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:06.28,0:08:08.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂 别这样叫我啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:09.08,0:08:11.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小Ec 就是小Ec呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:11.32,0:08:14.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哎 随便你啦 他们是谁？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:14.49,0:08:16.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Viola跟Cesario
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:16.79,0:08:17.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是她们俩人的同伴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:18.22,0:08:19.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那你们俩个怎么会来这里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:20.03,0:08:22.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是局长拜托我们偷偷保护你们的啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:23.16,0:08:26.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,陨石交给我们的Fenice扫除掉就行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:26.53,0:08:28.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们快点去Silvana
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:28.90,0:08:29.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的多谢了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:30.07,0:08:33.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没关系、没关系 不过你们之后得请客喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:33.54,0:08:35.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦？又得请？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:36.81,0:08:38.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦？中国菜？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:38.65,0:08:40.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,意大利菜比较好啦！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:41.82,0:08:43.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,之前不也是吃中国菜吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:43.72,0:08:45.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就决定吃意大利菜好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:45.59,0:08:46.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好期待、好期待喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:48.66,0:08:50.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们还是老样子一点都没变耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:50.76,0:08:52.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 我们永远都相亲相爱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:52.36,0:08:53.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小Lumi跟小Ec也很要好啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:53.46,0:08:54.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是比不上我跟Cesario
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:55.20,0:08:58.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,人是挺不错 只是很会精打细算罢了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:59.53,0:09:03.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,该怎么说呢…我觉得GOTT的人应该是更…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:03.67,0:09:05.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你以为我们是那种让人不能不绷紧神经的人 是吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:06.07,0:09:07.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊…不是的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:07.61,0:09:08.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,各种人都有啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:09.14,0:09:11.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不管是GOTT或是这世上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:19.85,0:09:22.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好了如果无法决定继承人的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:22.76,0:09:26.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,将由我们委员会全权负责今后的运营
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:26.49,0:09:27.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,说起来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:27.63,0:09:31.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在猎户座腕部区的经营收支这期也有盈余呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:31.63,0:09:32.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为那个区域的负责人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:33.07,0:09:35.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,代代都是由我们家的人所担任
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:36.04,0:09:36.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,经由这次的机会
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:37.17,0:09:41.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,应该能在财务掌管这方面获得更多的权责吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:43.24,0:09:43.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:44.14,0:09:45.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,锵～锵～
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:46.08,0:09:46.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,让大家久等了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:47.21,0:09:49.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rosenfelt财团的继承人到达
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:58.99,0:10:00.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这个隔间是干嘛用的呀？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:00.76,0:10:02.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,卫生防护罩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:02.66,0:10:03.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,卫生防护罩？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:28.66,0:10:30.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,监定完毕了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:30.66,0:10:32.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Timothy·Constance
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:32.39,0:10:33.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,经过确认 证实与
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:34.19,0:10:36.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Albert·Rosenfelt以及Marianne Constance
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:37.10,0:10:39.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,两人的DNA排序一致
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:41.50,0:10:43.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这样一来 事情应该会更没完没了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:48.84,0:10:51.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 看来是赶上了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:51.24,0:10:54.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,接下来似乎正在举行宴会的样子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:54.85,0:10:58.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对一定会再发生一些事情吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:59.95,0:11:01.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们就等着瞧吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:17.50,0:11:18.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么衣服啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:19.21,0:11:21.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这样就吃不到料理了呀!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:21.67,0:11:25.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,“贵族阶级”是以完全未接受过\N“身体适应处理”为傲的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:26.18,0:11:27.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,纯粹血统主义者
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:28.21,0:11:30.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rosenfelt家族也是其中之一
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:30.85,0:11:31.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们这些人对他们来说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:31.85,0:11:33.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只不过算是杂菌而已吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:34.75,0:11:36.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Timothy
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:36.29,0:11:39.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今后将在这些人之中生活
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:40.53,0:11:41.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,赛马？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:41.96,0:11:42.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:42.96,0:11:44.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,虽然骑马是妇女们的嗜好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:46.67,0:11:48.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但以机械马竞速 可是我们一族的传统
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:48.84,0:11:53.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只要是族里的男性 没有人不会的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:53.37,0:11:56.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,机械马是一项能测试出勇气与智慧的竞赛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:57.18,0:12:00.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请务必让我们拜见一下新统帅者的技巧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:00.58,0:12:03.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可、可是我对机械马…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:03.85,0:12:06.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哦 那真是失礼了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:06.75,0:12:10.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我都忘了你并没有受过贵族阶级的教育
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:11.09,0:12:12.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,听说你的父亲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:12.83,0:12:15.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,虽然身为我族的一员却在边境的开发中行星
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:15.66,0:12:18.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,被庶民的女孩给骗了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:18.83,0:12:21.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但遗传基因是骗不了人的吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:22.97,0:12:23.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要是我赢了赛马
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:24.14,0:12:26.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们就愿意承认我是继承人吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:26.91,0:12:27.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,当然
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:27.91,0:12:29.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不过 要是赢不了的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:29.71,0:12:32.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,希望你能够自行承认自己并没有继承的资格
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:33.08,0:12:33.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:34.21,0:12:36.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你想後悔？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:36.58,0:12:37.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:37.78,0:12:38.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,来人啊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:38.75,0:12:40.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快为族长备马
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:40.82,0:12:42.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没那个必要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:42.29,0:12:43.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:43.32,0:12:45.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Donnersclac借你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:45.26,0:12:48.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,给这些家伙们一点颜色瞧瞧吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:48.56,0:12:50.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可…可是 为什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:50.96,0:12:52.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,需要理由吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:53.07,0:12:54.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:54.23,0:12:56.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,跟我说的一样吧!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:56.44,0:12:57.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,的确…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:07.51,0:13:09.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想不到参加者变的这么多
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:09.82,0:13:12.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且他们都有老练的教官在指导
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:12.82,0:13:13.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没问题
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:14.22,0:13:17.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再怎么说也有我在嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:17.52,0:13:18.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊…是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:21.39,0:13:23.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他好像在盘算着什么喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:23.83,0:13:25.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你可务必要小心提防
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:25.87,0:13:26.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:38.44,0:13:40.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,做得不错喔 再提高一点速度
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:40.91,0:13:41.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喔…好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:45.49,0:13:47.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还蛮不赖的嘛 族长
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:47.32,0:13:49.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是庶民就要像个庶民
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:49.62,0:13:52.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还是在受伤之前快点回家去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:52.99,0:13:55.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,果然还是干这种小心眼的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:55.63,0:13:57.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,比赛总是伴随着危险
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:58.10,0:14:00.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,说起来这是贵族的嗜好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:00.27,0:14:01.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,庶民是不会懂的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:03.17,0:14:05.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,害怕吗？ 可别被甩下去了哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:13.75,0:14:16.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是给过分淘气的少爷们一点小小的惩罚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:18.32,0:14:20.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好厉害呀！Eclair
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:20.75,0:14:22.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你 Mr…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:22.39,0:14:24.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不对…嗯，这个…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:25.02,0:14:26.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,朋友们都叫我Tim
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:26.89,0:14:28.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,0K Tim
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:33.93,0:14:34.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tim 来了喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:36.87,0:14:38.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那一台也有参加吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:39.51,0:14:40.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是混在出场者之中的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:41.14,0:14:42.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那个完全是战斗用
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:42.68,0:14:43.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,专业级的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:43.58,0:14:44.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:45.38,0:14:46.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你负责操纵Donner
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:47.21,0:14:49.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们让我来负责
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:49.55,0:14:50.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:52.12,0:14:54.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是金融管理局的ES成员吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:54.72,0:14:58.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只有陨石的欢迎仪式还不够过瘾吗？同行的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:58.83,0:15:00.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,身为ES成员
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:00.26,0:15:03.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,却还以真面目示人似乎是你们GOTT的传统
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:03.66,0:15:05.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但这也是一件极度愚蠢的事情！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:05.37,0:15:07.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,蒙面是坏人才会做的事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:07.60,0:15:09.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,市场可是这么决定的哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:09.24,0:15:10.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tim 喷射
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:10.94,0:15:11.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:14.44,0:15:15.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别想逃！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:28.82,0:15:30.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Donner 钢丝腕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:33.66,0:15:35.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,搞这种鬼玩意儿…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:39.73,0:15:40.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,做得不错哦 Tim
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:41.53,0:15:43.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一定是你爸爸遗传给你的才能
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:54.71,0:15:55.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没事吧？ Tim
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:57.15,0:15:58.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,逮到了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:05.76,0:16:06.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Titano！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:07.53,0:16:08.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小Ec
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:09.93,0:16:11.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们也是GOTT的吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:15.80,0:16:17.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很遗憾啰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:17.37,0:16:20.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Titano的装甲是特制的呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:25.34,0:16:26.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,甩他出去！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:40.66,0:16:41.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这…这个是？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:42.53,0:16:44.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那两个人如果手牵手的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:44.46,0:16:47.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就可以控制分子的结合力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:47.57,0:16:47.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:48.10,0:16:50.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果手没有牵上的话就不行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:51.10,0:16:53.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谢啦 Cesario、Viola
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:55.94,0:16:57.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,任务完成
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:57.74,0:17:00.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再来就等你吃意大利料理啰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:00.58,0:17:02.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,呀…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:02.92,0:17:05.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cesario 手…手！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:06.72,0:17:07.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,唉呦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:09.46,0:17:10.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:10.39,0:17:12.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,中国菜、就吃中国菜好了啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:16.10,0:17:17.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,坏心眼 哼～
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:26.91,0:17:29.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,即使拥有一个出生于开发中星球的母亲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:29.74,0:17:32.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也同样能够具备勇气 这件事你们能接受了吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:35.18,0:17:39.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你父亲的选择似乎是正确的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:39.49,0:17:41.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,委任书…就交给你吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:44.22,0:17:45.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只要你们能了解就好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:52.17,0:17:53.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 Eclair
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:54.20,0:17:55.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,让你帮了我这么多忙 但…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:56.14,0:17:57.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没关系啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:57.54,0:18:00.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我…从一开始就打算这么做了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:01.07,0:18:07.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我只是想向他们这群人讨回妈妈的名誉而以
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:08.01,0:18:11.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你愿意再重新考虑一下吗？ Timothy
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:11.35,0:18:12.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:12.62,0:18:13.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,您是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:13.95,0:18:16.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是Isaac·Rosenfelt
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:16.42,0:18:17.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你的祖父
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:17.96,0:18:19.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:19.26,0:18:20.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,祖父？ 爷爷吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:21.19,0:18:22.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,会…会长！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:22.53,0:18:24.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,您不是在静养中吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:25.83,0:18:27.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且 将你的父亲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:27.90,0:18:31.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,从你的母亲身边夺走的 正是我本人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:31.37,0:18:33.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不会跟你道歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:33.61,0:18:37.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为财团需要Albert的力量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:37.64,0:18:41.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那 这么说来 爸爸并没有抛弃我们母子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:41.48,0:18:43.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,知道Albert的遗言後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:43.62,0:18:44.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,让我感到相当怀疑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:45.15,0:18:48.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你真的适合担任本财团的继承人吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:48.89,0:18:51.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以我觉得必须亲自测试看看才行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:52.06,0:18:52.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:52.86,0:18:56.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那 局长早就知道指定的是哪个星球啰？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:56.90,0:18:58.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没有错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:58.50,0:19:02.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是没想到这些家伙居然会如此的胡作非为
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:03.10,0:19:06.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,待会儿一定得好好的惩罚惩罚他们才行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:07.77,0:19:13.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我似乎已经能够理解爸爸为什么会单独回家族来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:13.28,0:19:14.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:14.75,0:19:17.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸比任何人都了解
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:17.48,0:19:20.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在平常环境下成长的人 要在贵族阶级中生活
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:20.52,0:19:22.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,会是件多么辛苦的事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:22.96,0:19:28.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸会离开我们母子这都是出自於爸爸对我们的爱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:28.93,0:19:31.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,即使如此 依然指定我为继承人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:32.13,0:19:37.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这一定也是为了让我能够对自己的人生有选择的自由
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:38.60,0:19:40.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是Tim…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:40.31,0:19:43.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你有权利选择自己的人生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:44.14,0:19:46.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,无论星星告诉了你什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:46.35,0:19:49.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你的道路 还是必须由你自己来决定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:51.22,0:19:54.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,虽然…我没办法马上做出决定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:54.39,0:19:55.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:56.12,0:20:00.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果因为没有族长而造成整个家族分崩离析的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:00.59,0:20:02.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还不如顺理继承比较好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:03.23,0:20:04.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:04.46,0:20:06.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在Timothy下定决心之前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:07.03,0:20:08.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,继承人的问题就先保留不谈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:09.20,0:20:11.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在这段期间内我会先辅助族长
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:12.20,0:20:15.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然后万一Timothy发生了什么意外
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:15.44,0:20:18.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就立刻将Rosenfelt财团分割解体
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:18.48,0:20:19.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就这么办！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:20.05,0:20:21.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:22.08,0:20:24.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你可以慢慢考虑的Tim
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:24.75,0:20:28.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为你的人生是属于你自己的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:28.32,0:20:29.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eclair…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:30.02,0:20:31.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eclair 我觉得你…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:32.19,0:20:33.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:34.03,0:20:35.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没事…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:46.21,0:20:48.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你都看到了吧？ Lumiere
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:48.87,0:20:52.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 希望你能好好的说明
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:54.61,0:20:56.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,影像证据？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:56.28,0:20:57.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:57.32,0:21:01.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,金融管理局妨碍我们工作的证据
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:01.59,0:21:03.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这下子 以后我们就能牵制他们了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:04.62,0:21:05.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是为了拍下这个影像
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:06.06,0:21:09.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以才让 Armbrust故意怂恿财团的人是吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:09.60,0:21:12.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,让他们以继承权为赌注展开比赛
